events.name: Georgia Tech Yellow Jackets at Louisville Cardinals

headlines.description: TaQuon Marshall ran for 175 yards and two scores to lead Georgia Tech to a 66-31 victory over Louisville on Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Marshall, Georgia Tech run all over Louisville 66-31

video.headline: Georgia Tech DB makes 95-yard INT return for TD

events.name: Middle Tennessee Blue Raiders at Marshall Thundering Herd

headlines.description: Brent Stockstill threw for 317 yards and two scores, going over 10,000 career yards passing, and Middle Tennessee beat Marshall 34-24 on Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Middle Tennessee's Stockstill hits 10,000 mark in 34-24 win

video.headline: Thomas' TD seals win for Middle Tennessee

events.name: Utah State Aggies at BYU Cougars

headlines.description: Jordan Love threw for a career-high four touchdowns and ran for another and Utah State beat BYU 45-20 Friday night, the Aggies' first back-to-back wins in the 88-game series since 1973-74.
headlines.shortLinkText: Love tosses 4 TD passes; Utah State beats BYU again, 45-20
